But #TwitterFoodBank has many of the same downsides as the use of GoFundMe and other crowdfunding vehicles to cover medical expenses and emergency bills.
How to provide relief to families suffering during the Covid-19 pandemicGiving through #TwitterFoodBank will certainly help some people, but many families who don’t use Twitter are suffering now, too.
And millions of other Americans have seen their wages reduced as hours and salaries are cut as cost-saving measures.